\c 18
\s Abhurahama anovimbiswa mwana
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakaonekwa kwaari pamiouki*\x + 13.18.\x* yeMamure iye agere pamusuwo wetende pakupisa kwezuva,
\v 2 ndokusimudza meso ake ndokuona, zvino tarira, varume vatatu\x + VaHeb. 13.2. Gen.. 18.22; 19.1; 31.11,13; 48.16. Eki. 3.2,14; 6.3; 14.19; 13.21; 24.10. Isa. 63.9. Mara. 3.1.\x* vamire naye; paaka\add va\add*ona wakamhanya kubva pamusuwo wetende kunovachingamidza\x + 19.1.\x*, ndokukotamira pasi,
\v 3 ndokuti: Ishe, kana ikozvino ndawana nyasha pameso penyu, musapfuura henyu kubva pamuranda wenyu.
\v 4 Ngakuuiswe hako mvura shoma\x + 19.2; 24.32; 43.24.\x*, mugoshambidza tsoka dzenyu, uye muzembere pasi pemuti.
\v 5 Zvino ndichaunza chimedu chechingwa\x + Vato. 6.18; 13.15.\x*, mugosimbisa moyo yenyu; shure kwaizvozvo mopfuura, nokuti ndizvo zvamapfuurira nekumuranda wenyu\x + 19.8; 33.10.\x*. Ivo ndokuti: Ita saizvozvo sezvawataura.
\v 6 Abhurahama ndokukurumidza kuenda mutende kuna Sara, ndokuti: Kurumidza \add ugadzire\add* zviyero zvitatu zveupfu hwakatsetseka! Kanya, ugoita makeke.
\v 7 Abhurahama ndokumhanyira kumombe, ndokutora mhuru \add ine nyama\add* yakapfava uye yakanaka, ndokupa kujaya; iro ndokukurumidza kuigadzira.
\v 8 Zvino wakatora mukaka wakafa, nemukaka mumbishi, nemhuru yaaiva agadzira, ndokuunza pamberi pavo; ndokumira pedo navo muzasi memuti, ivo ndokudya.
\p
\v 9 Ivo ndokuti kwaari: Uripi Sara mukadzi wako? Iye ndokuti: Tarirai, mutende\x + 24.67.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino wakati: Zvirokwazvo ndichadzoka kwauri nenguva \add iyi\add* yeupenyu\x + 18.14.\x*; zvino tarira, Sara mukadzi wako a\add chava\add* nemwanakomana\x + 17.19,21; 21.2. VaRom. 9.9.\x*. Sarawo aka\add zvi\add*nzwa ari pamusuwo wetende waiva shure kwake.
\v 11 Zvino Abhurahama naSara vaiva vakwegura, vava nemakore mazhinji\x + 17.17. VaRom. 4.19. VaHeb. 11.11,12,19.\x*. Mutoo wevakadzi waiva waguma\x + 31.35.\x* kuna Sara.
\v 12 Naizvozvo Sara wakaseka mukati make\x + 17.17. Ruk. 1.18.\x* achiti: Ndakwegura, ndingava nemufaro here, naishe wangu\x + 1 Pet. 3.6.\x* achemberawo?
\v 13 Jehovha ndokuti kuna Abhurahama: Sara wasekerei achiti: Zvirokwazvo ndichabereka ini ndakwegura here?
\v 14 Kune chinhu chinorema kukunda Jehovha\x + Jer. 32.17. Zek. 8.6. Mat. 19.26. Ruk. 1.37.\x* here? Nenguva yakatarwa ndichadzoka kwauri\x + 17.21; 18.10. 2 Madz. 4.16.\x*, nenguva \add ino \add*yeupenyu, uye Sara achava nemwanakomana.
\v 15 Sara ndokuramba\x + Rev. 19.11.\x* achiti: Handina kuseka; nokuti waitya. Asi \add iye\add* wakati: Kwete asi waseka.
\s Abhurahama anonyengeterera Sodhoma
\p
\v 16 Zvino varume vakasimuka kubva ipapo ndokutarira pasi kuSodhoma; Abhurahama ndokuenda navo kuvaperekedza\x + VaRom. 15.24. 3 Joh. 6.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino Jehovha wakati: Ndichavanzira Abhurahama zvandinoita\x + Map. 25.14. Amo. 3.7. Joh. 15.15.\x* here?
\v 18 Nokuti zvirokwazvo Abhurahama achava rudzi rukuru uye rwune simba; uye marudzi ose enyika acharopafadzwa nemaari\x + 12.3; 22.18; 26.4. Mab. 3.25. VaGar. 3.8.\x*.
\v 19 Nokuti ndamuziva, kuti araire vana vake\x + Det. 4.9,10; 6.7. VaEfe. 6.4.\x* neimba yake\x + 17.27. Josh. 24.15.\x* shure kwake, vagochengeta nzira yaJehovha kuita kururama nekutonga; kuti Jehovha aunze pamusoro paAbhurahama izvo zvaakataura maererano naye.
\v 20 Jehovha ndokuti: Nokuti kuchema kweSodhoma neGomora kukuru\x + 4.10; 19.13. Jak. 5.4.\x*, uye nokuti chivi chavo chinorema zvikuru,
\v 21 ndichaburuka\x + 11.5. Eki. 3.8.\x* ikozvino ndigoona kana vakaita zvizere zvinoenderana nekuchema kwaro kwasvika kwandiri; asi kana zvisina \add kudaro\add*, ndichaziva\x + Det. 8.2; 13.3.\x*.
\v 22 Zvino varume vakafuratira ipapo, ndokuenda kuSodhoma\x + 19.1.\x*; asi Abhurahama waiva achakamira pamberi paJehovha\x + 18.1.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Zvino Abhurahama wakaswedera\x + VaHeb. 10.22.\x*, ndokuti: Muchaparadzawo wakarurama pamwe newakaipa\x + 20.4. Num. 16.22. 2 Sam. 24.17.\x* here?
\v 24 Zvimwe varipo vakarurama makumi mashanu mukati meguta; muchaparadzawo mukasaregerera nzvimbo nekuda kwevakarurama makumi mashanu vari mariri here?
\v 25 Ngazvive kure nemwi kuita chinhu chakadaro, kuuraya wakarurama pamwe newakaipa, kuti wakarurama ave sewakaipa\x + Job. 8.20.\x*; ngazvive kure nemwi. Mutongi wenyika yose haangaiti zvakarurama here\x + Job. 8.3. VaRom. 3.6.\x*?
\p
\v 26 Jehovha ndokuti: Kana ndikawana muSodhoma vakarurama makumi mashanu mukati meguta\x + Jer. 5.1. Eze. 22.30.\x*, ipapo ndicharegerera nzvimbo yose nekuda kwavo.
\v 27 Zvino Abhurahama wakapindura\x + Ruk. 18.1.\x* ndokuti: Tarirai henyu, ndazvipira kutaura kuna Ishe kunyange ndiri guruva nedota\x + 2.7; 3.19. Job. 4.19.\x*.
\v 28 Zvimwe kuchashaikwa vashanu kuvakarurama makumi mashanu; muchaparadza guta rose nekuda kwevashanu here? Iye ndokuti: Handingariparadzi kana ndikawanamo makumi mana nevashanu.
\v 29 Zvino wakaramba achitaurazve naye ndokuti: Zvimwe kuchawanikwamo makumi mana. Iye ndokuti: Handinga\add zvi\add*iti nekuda kwemakumi mana.
\v 30 Zvino wakati: Ishe ngaarege hake kutsamwa, apo ndichitaura. Zvimwe makumi matatu vachawanikwamo. Iye ndokuti: Handinga\add zvi\add*iti kana ndikawanamo makumi matatu.
\v 31 Zvino wakati: Tarira ikozvino, ndazvipira kutaura kuna Ishe; zvimwe kuchawanikwamo makumi maviri. Iye ndokuti: Handinga\add ri\add*paradzi nekuda kwemakumi maviri.
\v 32 Zvino wakati: Ishe ngaarege hake kutsamwa\x + Vato. 6.39.\x*, ndichataurazve ikozvino kamwe; zvimwe kuchawanikwamo gumi. Iye ndokuti: Handinga\add ri\add*paradzi nekuda kwevane gumi.
\v 33 Zvino Jehovha wakafamba paaiva apedza kutaura naAbhurahama; Abhurahama ndokudzokera kunzvimbo yake.